cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.IR 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CL (Computation and Language) - This paper deals with natural language processing and specifically focuses on paraphrase generation, which falls under the scope of cs.CL. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper proposes a novel neural approach for paraphrase generation using deep learning models, which falls under the scope of cs.LG. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper proposes a new approach for generating paraphrases using deep learning models, which falls under the scope of cs.AI. 
4. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) - The paper proposes a stacked residual LSTM network for efficient training of deep LSTMs, which falls under the scope of cs.NE. 
5. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) - The paper evaluates the performance of the proposed model and other state-of-the-art deep learning models on different datasets using various evaluation metrics, which falls under the scope of cs.IR.
